There hasn't been as much of a need, so we were able to give back to the city. And I suspect that we will see that year after year as those numbers continue to fall. And that's pretty much across the state, is that we're seeing those numbers come down. So I was able to give back $20,000 from last year for that line item. Office supplies stayed the same. We came down on travel and conferences.

19
