or the Navy and Marine Corps. We celebrate or we participated in Wreaths Across America for the first time. We exceeded our goal and we have doubled that for this coming year. We've been invited back so we're going to participate again this year. We'll be kicking that off in July with a Christmas in July promotion.

47
00:23:04,692 --> 00:23:22,748
Our goal is 500, I would love to get up to 1,000. I think if we promote it a little bit more, that is a reasonable expectation. There was definitely a lot of really good feedback from last year. I'm excited to do that again.

48
